ClassDesc: This interface is only used by implementations of com.google.ads.mediation.MediationAdapter, which has been deprecated in favor of @B_com#google#android#gms#ads#mediation#MediationAdapter_E@. Extras for new mediation adapters are passed in as a @B_android#os#Bundle_E@ through @B_com#google#android#gms#ads#AdRequest#Builder#addNetworkExtrasBundle_E@. An empty interface for use by Google Mobile Ads mediation adapters. There are intentionally no methods to implement. This interface is deprecated.
